                  <td width="277" height="59" valign="top"><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Respected 
                    Hollywood movie critic Welford Beaton seriously predicted 
                    that talkies would become a major fiasco. <br>
                    Audiences would rather use their imagination and therefore 
                    they would want go back to the silent films. </font></td>
