                  <td width="321" height="59" valign="top"> 
                    <p><font size="4" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Edison 
                      - The Invention of the Movies (1891-1918) </font></p>
                    <p>140 of the first moving pictures ever seen, spanning the 
                      birth of cinema from 1891-1918 (4 discs)</p>
                    <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">&gt;&gt; 
                      <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/search?ie=UTF8&keywords=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FEdison-Invention-Movies-1891-1918-Thomas%2Fdp%2FB0006Q93LA%2Fref%3Dpd%5Fbbs%5Fsr%5F1%2F104-0782807-6643913%3Fie%3DUTF8%26amp%3Bs%3Ddvd%26amp%3Bqid%3D1177863230%26amp%3Bsr%3D1-1&tag=filmsounddesign&index=blended&linkCode=ur2&camp=1789&creative=9325">Amazon.com</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=filmsounddesign&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=1" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" /></font></p>
                    <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">&gt;&gt; 
                      <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/redirect.html?ie=UTF8&location=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FEdison-Invention-Movies-REGION-NTSC%2Fdp%2FB0006Q93LA%3Fie%3DUTF8%26s%3Ddvd%26qid%3D1177863614%26sr%3D1-2&tag=filmsound-21&linkCode=ur2&camp=1634&creative=6738">Amazon 
                      UK</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.co.uk/e/ir?t=filmsound-21&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=2" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" /> 
                      </font></p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
